text: I like that the kids are motivated with the Koko coins!

I went to koobits website and am so impressed! I particularly love that the questions are broken down and explained in colourful diagrams and models, with step by step guidance to solve the questions. Definitely beats me monotonous, sometimes angry explanations hands down. What's more, it is able to identify the child's strengths and weaknesses to provide personalised practices!I have always been a weak student when I was younger, if only that was such a learning resource at my time. 😭
